<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>měi yī tiān měi yī wǎn fēn miǎo zhī jiān 迦南593</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 měi yī tiān měi yī wǎn fēn miǎo zhī jiān tiān fù dōu huì zài àn zhōng chá kàn
 wǒ yī yán wǒ yī xíng dōu bù néng yǐn mán dōu xiǎn lù zài fù shén de miàn qián
 rén dōu ài zuò shì qíng zuò gěi rén kàn què bù néng mò mò de shě jǐ fèng xiàn
 dān yǒu wài miàn duō me kě lián zhǔ a qiú nǐ jiāng wǒ gǎi biàn
 jiāng wǒ de xīn chéng xiàn zài nǐ miàn qián lì zhì měi rì qīng zhèng jìng qián
 zhè yàng wǒ kě yǐ tǎn rán wú jù lái dào shī ēn de bǎo zuò qián</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>593</hymn_number>
</song>